structure.unit: FEES AND COMPENSATION OF PUBLIC OFFICERS AND EMPLOYEES

law.history: Repealed 1976 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 17, sec. 52, effective January 1, 1978. -- Amended 1976 Ky. Acts ch. 62, sec. 63. -- Amended 1968 Ky. Acts ch. 149, sec. 1. -- Created 1966 Ky. Acts ch. 255, sec. 72.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Compensation of assistants and stenographers of commonwealth's attorney in counties of 200,000.
